description: This file is the entry point for a React application. It imports core React libraries, CSS styles, and the main App component. It initializes the React DOM renderer and mounts the App component under the DOM element with id 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering React components in the specified DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the root DOM node.
